      "content": "thx for that. that's actually a pretty solid start. i'm curious though, when you say the \"stereotypical black\" character is often a \"thug,\" can u expand on that? like, what are the specific traits or ways they usually act in these movies? just trying to get the specific \"vibe\" right so i can mock it effectively in the script.",
